<h3><a href="/casestudies.cfm">Case Studies</a></h3>
<label>January 9, 2024<br/><b><a class="descriptor" href="issuedetail.cfm?issue=3640326">Volume 21, issue 6 </a></b></label>
<p>

&nbsp;
<a href="https://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=3639448">
<img src="img/icon_pdf.png" alt="Download PDF version of this article" />
PDF
</a>
